description: Appropriately dubbed the ‘Antonio Banderas’ of food trucks, the Tex’s Tacos food truck is nothing short of suavé – a fully equipped kitchen & restaurant on wheels. Serving-up a delicious array of ‘Nueva Texicana’ eats with style and grace, we’re bringing the fun & excitement of the Tex’s Tacos experience directly to the people. Keep your head on a swivel, because you never know when the fiesta might roll-up to your neck of the woods!
name: Tex's Tacos
